OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,FWith the war in Iran about to enter
OL,7,Fits fifth week, some mortgage offers
OL,8,Fhave started trickling back onto the
OL,9,Fmarket - but at much higher rates than
OL,10,Fbefore.
OL,12,FHundreds of deals disappeared from the
OL,13,Fmarket amid changing expectations for
OL,14,Ffinancial markets, with inflation in
OL,15,Fthe UK forecast to be higher than
OL,16,Fpredicted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
