OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,FThe average two-year fixed-rate
OL,7,Fhomeowner mortgage has now increased
OL,8,Fto the highest average rate since
OL,9,FAugust 2024, financial information
OL,10,Fwebsite Moneyfacts said.
OL,12,FMeanwhile five-year fixed-rate
OL,13,Fmortgages have risen to their highest
OL,14,Frate since December 2023.
OL,16,FThere are 1,620 fewer deals on the
OL,17,Fmarket than there were when lenders
OL,18,Fbegan pulling deals on March 9, Adam
OL,19,FFrench, head of consumer finance at
OL,20,FMoneyfacts, said - but 160 more have
OL,21,Fbeen added since March 25.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
