OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774663388
OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,F"Mortgage rates have continued to rise
OL,7,Fsharply, with around three in four
OL,8,Factive lenders increasing rates,
OL,9,Flaunching or withdrawing products this
OL,10,Fweek," French said.
OL,12,FHere is a snapshot of the mortgage
OL,13,Fmarket as of Saturday, March 27,
OL,14,Faccording to Moneyfacts:
OL,16,FThere are currently 6,016 residential
OL,17,Fmortgage products available, up from
OL,18,F5,990 the previous working day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
