OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,FMultiple mortgage lenders met with
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves on Thursday,
OL,8,Fand a commitment was made to
OL,9,Fproactively contact the 1.6 million
OL,10,Fcustomers whose fixed-rate deals will
OL,11,Ffinish between now and the end of 2026.
OL,13,FLenders will set out customers'
OL,14,Foptions and how to access bespoke
OL,15,Fsupport, the Treasury said.
OL,17,FThe lenders also reaffirmed the
OL,18,FMortgage Charter, which helps to
OL,19,Fensure borrowers in difficulty receive
OL,20,Fsupport, but French warned this might
OL,21,Fnot go far enough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
