OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774663388
OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,F"Getting lenders to recommit to the
OL,7,Fcharter is welcome news at a time when
OL,8,Fmany households are facing a sharp
OL,9,Frise in borrowing costs," French said.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,F"If these measures are fully back in
OL,17,Fplay, they can offer borrowers some
OL,18,Fflexibility, but it's important to be
OL,19,Fclear that they often come with very
OL,20,Freal trade-offs."
