OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,FMany borrowers coming up for
OL,7,Fremortgage are now facing the prospect
OL,8,Fof paying "thousands of pounds more
OL,9,Fper year" than they would have
OL,10,Fexpected just a few weeks ago, French
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"For some, this support may help keep
OL,14,Ftheir budgets just about manageable,
OL,15,Fbut it won't remove the financial
OL,16,Fstrain altogether," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
