OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,FA spokesperson for UK Finance said:
OL,7,F"Mortgage lenders provide a wide range
OL,8,Fof support to their customers. Help
OL,9,Fwill always be available and anyone
OL,10,Fworried about their mortgage should
OL,11,Fget in touch with their lender as
OL,12,Fearly as possible."
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
